(24, 1, '2023-10-06 16:22:35', '2023-10-06 16:22:35', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>JavaScript is a versatile and widely-used programming language primarily employed in web development. It allows developers to add interactivity, manipulate web page content, and respond to user actions within web browsers. JavaScript is essential for creating dynamic and engaging web applications by enabling tasks such as form validation, animations, real-time updates, and more. It is a client-side scripting language, meaning it runs in the user\'s browser, reducing the need for constant communication with the web server. JavaScript can also be used on the server-side, thanks to technologies like Node.js, making it a powerful tool for full-stack web development.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Javascript', 'These are javascript tutorials', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'javascript', '', '', '2023-10-06 16:22:35', '2023-10-06 16:22:35', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=24', 0, 'post', '', 0),
