(42, 1, '2023-10-06 16:31:53', '2023-10-06 16:31:53', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Python is a versatile and high-level programming language known for its simplicity and readability. It is widely used in various domains, including web development, data science, artificial intelligence, scientific computing, and more. Python\'s clean and expressive syntax makes it easy for developers to write and maintain code.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Key features of Python include dynamic typing, automatic memory management, and a comprehensive standard library that provides ready-to-use modules and packages for a wide range of tasks. Python\'s extensive ecosystem includes popular frameworks like Django and Flask for web development, as well as libraries like NumPy, pandas, and TensorFlow for data analysis and machine learning.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Python\'s versatility, cross-platform compatibility, and a large and active community of developers have contributed to its popularity and widespread adoption in the world of programming.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Phyton', 'These are phyton tutorials', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'phyton', '', '', '2023-10-06 16:31:53', '2023-10-06 16:31:53', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=42', 0, 'post', '', 0),
